{"article_id":"RM4JnvoVbpodG7Yx","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Democrats know","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Trump ' s greatest legacy may be the ascent of a second conservative supreme court justice .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Their fight","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"to stop it","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"starts now","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"Is he the unassuming family man","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"who talks baseball over a beer ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"champions working women","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"and directs traffic at the Fourth of July parade ?","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Or the extreme ideologue","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"whose ascent will strike a hammer blow to women ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"tilt America to the right for a generation","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"and shore up the re-election of Donald Trump ?","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Should Kavanaugh occupy the swing vote seat ?","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"His judicial record says no |","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Shira A Scheindlin","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"Read more","depth":3},{"id":17,"text":"The opposing portraits of Brett Kavanaugh the man and Brett Kavanaugh the jurist will collide on Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"when the Senate considers him for the supreme court .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"The confirmation hearing , a critical test of temperament , may illuminate","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"whether he is ultimately driven by the law or by ideology .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Either way , the seat is Kavanaugh ' s to lose .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Liberal activists have found it hard to sustain the fury","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that followed his nomination by Trump after swing vote Anthony Kennedy ' s retirement in June .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"The hearing on Capitol Hill represents Democrats ' last best chance","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"to thwart him .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"\" The only hope","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"the country has","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"is that Democrats will treat Kavanaugh like a hostile witness on the witness stand under cross-examination ,","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"throw him off script","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"and break him down , \"","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"said Francis Boyle , a law professor at the University of Illinois .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"\" You do not need a gentleman or gentlewoman","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"to deal with Kavanaugh .","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"You need a district attorney .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"Some Democrats are going to have to go for the jugular . \"","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"But Kavanaugh , 53 , is no Daniel in the lions ' den .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"He is the ultimate Washington insider ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"steeped in the city ' s political and legal establishments .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"His father spent more than two decades in the city as a lobbyist for the cosmetics industry .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"His mother was a high school teacher and a Maryland judge .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"An only child , Kavanaugh went to all-male Catholic schools ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"studied at Yale University and Yale Law School ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"clerked for Kennedy in 1993-94","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"and was an associate counsel for the independent counsel Kenneth Starr .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"In 1998 , two days before President Bill Clinton testified to a grand jury from the White House ,","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"Kavanaugh posed 10 suggested questions about the affair with Monica Lewinsky , many of them sexually explicit .","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"He ' s an extremely impressive jurist and the type of judge","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"you want a Republican president to nominate","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Greg Chernack","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"He was a member of Lawyers for Bush-Cheney during the 2000 election","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"and took part in the Florida recount","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"that gave George W Bush victory over Al Gore .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Kavanaugh served as a White House counsel to Bush and then staff secretary until 2006 ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"when","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"- his nomination having been held up by Democrats for three years -","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"he was appointed to the US court of appeals for the DC circuit .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"Once he became a judge ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"he decided to stop voting .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"He offered an insight into his judicial philosophy during a speech at Catholic University ' s law school in 2015 .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"He likened being a judge to being a good umpire ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"able to walk in others ' shoes","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"and understand them","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"while keeping emotions in check .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"\" On the bench ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"to put it in the vernacular ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"don ' t be a jerk , \"","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"also advising :","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"\" Check those political allegiances at the door","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"when you become a judge . \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Kavanaugh ' s supporters have been quick to point out","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"that he hired more female than male clerks .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"Sarah Pitlyk ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"who became a mother","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"shortly before clerking for Kavanaugh in 2010-11 ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"recently told an audience at the Heritage Foundation","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"how he called her","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"before the job started .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"\" He just put it out there","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"and said ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"' You ' re a mom","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"coming to clerk ,","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"I haven ' t done this before ,","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"you haven ' t done this before ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"let ' s figure out what we need to do","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"to make the clerkship just as rewarding for you","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"as it would be otherwise","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"but also to make it possible for you to be a mother","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"while you ' re doing it . ' \"","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"Kavanaugh supreme court nomination not 'normal ' ,","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"says Senate Democrat","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"Read more","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"She added :","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"\" He asked for my ideas","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"about how to do that .","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"He didn ' t tell me what would work for me ,","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"he didn ' t prescribe the best solution","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"based on his infinite wisdom or what he ' d seen in other contexts ...","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"We made the accommodations","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"that I needed to see my son every day","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"and also be clerk for Judge Kavanaugh . \"","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"The judge lives with his wife of 14 years , Ashley Estes Kavanaugh , and daughters Margaret and Elizabeth in a $ 1.2m home in Chevy Chase , an affluent , predominantly white town north of Washington .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"( According to the New York Times ,","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"he makes $ 220,600 as a federal judge","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"while she earns about $ 60,000 as town manager ) .","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"Kavanaugh is seen out walking his dog , Murphy , or shovelling snow .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"He has coached girls ' basketball teams","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"and serves as a lector and usher at Blessed Sacrament church .","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"Greg Chernack , a Democrat , lawyer and chairman of the town council , said :","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"\" He is very unassuming .","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"He ' s very down to earth and easy to talk to .","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"He ' s just another one of the neighbours .","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"He usually plays traffic cop on 4 July","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"when we have a parade . \"","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"Kavanaugh is a fan of Bruce Springsteen and the Washington Nationals baseball team ,","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"Chernack added .","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"\" I sense","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"he ' s a big reader and right upfront in knowing legal literature .","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"There are many things","depth":15},{"id":120,"text":"I disagree with him on","depth":15},{"id":121,"text":"but he ' s an extremely impressive jurist","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"and the type of judge","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"you want a Republican president to nominate . \"","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"Others","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"who have met him","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"also sing his praises .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"Curt Levey , president of the conservative activist group the Committee for Justice , said :","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"\" He ' s intellectually curious .","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"He loves to get into the details of the law","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"and that ' s why he loves being a judge .","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"He ' s the perfect person for it . \"","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"There has also been support from unexpected quarters .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"Lisa Blatt , a self-declared liberal Democrat and feminist","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"who has argued 35 cases before the supreme court , more than any other woman ,","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"wrote in Politico earlier this month :","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"\" Sometimes a superstar is just a superstar .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"That is the case with Judge Brett Kavanaugh ...","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"he will do the job with dignity , intelligence , empathy and integrity . \"","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"Kavanaugh seems likely to have the full support of the Senate ' s Republican majority","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"including Susan Collins of Maine and Lisa Murkowski of Alaska ,","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"having apparently assuaged their concerns over the landmark abortion rights ruling Roe v Wade .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Levey said :","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"\" It ' s one thing to say","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"it was wrongly decided .","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"It ' s another to say , after nearly 50 years ,","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"' I ' m going to go out there","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"and overturn it . '","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"He has used the Roberts dodge","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"of saying","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"Roe is settled law .","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"So what ?","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"The supreme court can unsettle it tomorrow","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"Francis Boyle , University of Illinois","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"\" I never got the sense","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"it ' s at the top of his list of the most important issues in the world .","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"The reason","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"there ' s no real doubt","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"Collins and Murkowski are going to vote for him","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"is they know that .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"He might be conservative","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"but he ' s not on an ideological mission","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"to ban all abortions . \"","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"Progressive activists , however , remain convinced","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"that is precisely his mission .","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"A multimillion-dollar advertising and lobbying campaign is in full swing .","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"The groups Women ' s March and Center for Popular Democracy Action are planning a day of action in Washington on Tuesday .","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"Boyle , an international law expert","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"who serves as counsel to Bosnia and Herzegovina and the provisional government of the Palestinian Authority ,","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"shares these concerns .","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"\" I think","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"Kavanaugh was put on there","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"to ensure","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":"Roe is overturned , \"","depth":14},{"id":174,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"\" He has used the Roberts dodge","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"of saying","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"it is settled law .","depth":14},{"id":178,"text":"So what ?","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"The supreme court can unsettle it tomorrow .","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"He did not say","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"it was decided correctly . \"","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"Critics note","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"that Trump has relied heavily on the rightwing Heritage Foundation and Federalist Society","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"to develop his shortlist for supreme court nominations .","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"Boyle said :","depth":12},{"id":186,"text":"\" Kavanaugh is an extreme ideologue and a legal hatchet man for the Federalist Society .","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"He was their spear carrier for years .","depth":14},{"id":188,"text":"He is being put on there by Trump","depth":15},{"id":189,"text":"to do their business","depth":16},{"id":190,"text":"and make the court as far right","depth":17},{"id":191,"text":"as he can under the circumstances .","depth":17},{"id":192,"text":"It ' s going to be bad for a lot of people :","depth":15},{"id":193,"text":"for gays , for African Americans , for labour , for women . \"","depth":15},{"id":194,"text":"Trump ' s nominations of solid conservatives Neil Gorsuch and Kavanaugh to the supreme court are the glue","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"holding his Republican coalition together ,","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"delighting evangelicals","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"and persuading at least some moderates to overlook the president ' s multiple shortcomings .","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"Come Tuesday , Democrats are likely to press Kavanaugh on Roe v Wade and LGBT rights , his scepticism about affirmative action , whether he misled senators at his 2006 confirmation hearings about national security issues in the Bush White House , and his attitude","depth":9},{"id":199,"text":"to whether a sitting president should be protected from litigation and criminal investigations .","depth":9},{"id":200,"text":"The decision by the Trump administration","depth":10},{"id":201,"text":"to withhold 100,000 documents","depth":11},{"id":202,"text":"relating to Kavanaugh ' s White House service","depth":11},{"id":203,"text":"will also hang over the hearing .","depth":9},{"id":204,"text":"Brett Kavanaugh had graphic questions for Bill Clinton about Lewinsky affair","depth":7},{"id":205,"text":"Read more","depth":8},{"id":206,"text":"Senators with courtroom backgrounds such as Richard Blumenthal of Connecticut and Kamala Harris of California are likely to probe hard .","depth":9},{"id":207,"text":"But John Malcolm , vice-president of the Institute for Constitutional Government at the Heritage Foundation , said :","depth":10},{"id":208,"text":"\" Judge Kavanaugh has been through two confirmation hearings","depth":12},{"id":209,"text":"and he ' s been battle tested .","depth":12},{"id":210,"text":"If he can serve in the positions","depth":13},{"id":211,"text":"he ' s served in in the Bush White House ,","depth":13},{"id":212,"text":"my guess is","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"he ' ll have no trouble at his confirmation hearing . \"","depth":13},{"id":214,"text":"Neal Katyal , an acting solicitor general in the Obama administration , predicted","depth":9},{"id":215,"text":"that the spotlight will be more on the nominee ' s conservatism than his character .","depth":9},{"id":216,"text":"\" Judge Kavanaugh is one of the most respected judges","depth":11},{"id":217,"text":"currently serving , \"","depth":11},{"id":218,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"\" At the same time , he ' s also conservative , and quite a bit more conservative than the justice","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"he has been nominated to replace . \"","depth":10},{"id":221,"text":"Kavanaugh ' s significance is likely to endure","depth":9},{"id":222,"text":"long after the latest outlandish speech or tweet from the president has been forgotten .","depth":9},{"id":223,"text":"Katyal , a law professor at Georgetown University in Washington , added :","depth":9},{"id":224,"text":"\" The stakes are astronomical -","depth":10},{"id":225,"text":"this nomination ,","depth":12},{"id":226,"text":"if successful ,","depth":12},{"id":227,"text":"will dramatically alter the composition of the US supreme court ,","depth":12},{"id":228,"text":"and very well may be President Trump ' s most lasting legacy . \"","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":457,"left":233,"right":456,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":233,"left":230,"right":232,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":230,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":232,"left":231,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":231,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":456,"left":244,"right":455,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":244,"left":243,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":242,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":240,"right":241,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":236,"right":239,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":236,"left":5,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":6,"right":234,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":234,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":239,"left":9,"right":238,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":10,"right":237,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":237,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":241,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":455,"left":297,"right":454,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":262,"right":296,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":247,"right":261,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":247,"left":245,"right":246,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":261,"left":21,"right":260,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":248,"right":259,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":22,"right":23,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":249,"right":258,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":24,"right":25,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":254,"right":257,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":253,"right":31,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":250,"right":252,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":250,"left":26,"right":27,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":28,"right":251,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":251,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":257,"left":256,"right":35,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":255,"right":34,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":255,"left":32,"right":33,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":272,"right":295,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":272,"left":36,"right":271,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":271,"left":263,"right":270,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":37,"right":38,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":264,"right":269,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":264,"left":39,"right":40,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":269,"left":41,"right":268,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":268,"left":42,"right":267,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":267,"left":265,"right":266,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":265,"left":43,"right":44,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":266,"left":45,"right":46,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":295,"left":274,"right":294,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":274,"left":273,"right":49,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":282,"right":293,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":282,"left":280,"right":281,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":280,"left":276,"right":279,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":276,"left":50,"right":275,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":275,"left":51,"right":52,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":53,"right":278,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":278,"left":54,"right":277,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":277,"left":55,"right":56,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":281,"left":57,"right":58,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":293,"left":290,"right":292,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity"